title: 5 things we learnt from Super Eagles' 1-0 win over Egypt
body:
5 things we learnt from Super Eagles’ 1-0 win over Egypt

The Super Eagles of Nigeria on Tuesday March 26 beat Egypt 1-0 in a friendly game at the Stephen Keshi Stadium in Asaba.

It was a Paul Onuachu goal just after nine seconds that gave the Super Eagles the win.
These are five things we learnt from that game.
1: Onuachu is quality

Not that his quality was in doubt by people who really know him. Onuachu has been the most…

summary: See when Solskjaer is to be appointed as Man United's permanent manager
title: See when Solskjaer is to be appointed as Man United's permanent manager
body:
See when Solskjaer is to be appointed as Man United’s permanent manager

Manchester United will announce the appointment of caretaker coach, Ole Gunnar Solskjaer, as the club’s new permanent manager before the end of this week.

Daily Mail reports that Man United’s hierarchy have reportedly already stopped their search for a new permanent manager and now regards Solskjaer as their one and only candidate to take the job.

Solskjaer has won 10 out of the 13 Premier League…
